<h3 class="sectionedit8" id="image">Image</h3>
<div class="level3">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> <a href="http://www.gtk-apps.org/content/show.php/Resize+Image?content=110541" class="urlextern" title="http://www.gtk-apps.org/content/show.php/Resize+Image?content=110541"  rel="nofollow">Changer la taille des images.</a> Resize Image</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Ajouter &quot;Redimensionner les images…&quot; dans le menu contextuel des images. <a href="tutoriel/comment_installer_un_paquet" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_installer_un_paquet">Installez le paquet</a> <strong><a href="apt://nautilus-image-converter" class="interwiki iw_apt" title="apt://nautilus-image-converter">nautilus-image-converter</a></strong> puis redémarrer la session.</div>
